{"tid":1565543,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"仲想抗爭既入一入黎，有平日防裝建議。","createTime":"2019-09-13T07:47:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T06:26:44.000Z","uid":263448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c6501263040a512acb5b05889f461b103e948254","tid":1565543,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:47:15.000Z","msg":"1.今晚快啲印文宣比手足貼連儂，唔好再專注係拖手同唱歌，<span style=\"color: red;\">出黎唱歌萬幾人，無幾多人貼文宣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"color: red;\">任何類型既抗爭活動，都要帶各地國旗</span>，唔好只舉美國、港英！！913,915,929,101咁。<br />\n<br />\n3.和理可以，但<span style=\"color: red;\">警方係你和理果陣，回晒血</span>！！<br />\n藍絲狗照樣丟漒水、玩刀！！！所以唔好成星期都和理！<br />\n得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外一啲個人防具裝備要帶下：<br />\n1.安全鞋<br />\n2.軍用皮帶<br />\n3.硬幣+襪<br />\n4.火機<br />\n5.鎖匙<br />\n呢啲行街都可以着/帶，無咁起眼，得閒練下踢腿，鞭技，跑步。<br />\n<br />\n安全鞋最基本，最好買防油防滑果類，<span style=\"color: red;\">鋼頭踢到人真係唔係幾覺痛</span>，呢啲實用鞋，好過啲運動鞋囉！<br />\n見好多和理非仲着布鞋膠鞋，一來款式易認，二來無乜防禦力攻擊力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z6MT1Tt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz6MT1Tt.jpg&h=2c44915a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個款除得快，平時都幾實用，帶有一定硬度，近遠佳宜，可以古惑破防，亦可以直斬當棍用，視乎鞭法。<br />\n雖然對全副武裝無乜用，但<span style=\"color: red;\">對付普通暴徒</span>足夠有餘。<br />\n因為有一定硬度，所以入皮帶果陣，少入幾個位，增加鬆帶速度比較好。<br />\n練鞭果陣，要諗點樣防搶，點打要害，<span style=\"color: red;\">小心唔好打頭</span>，打手腕手肘擊落對方武器就好。<br />\n<br />\n至於襪、火機、鎖匙、硬幣，除咗火機帶太多會比龜捉之外，其他都有合理理由。<br />\n但相對皮帶，呢啲裝備都要近戰用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yCNoEQJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyCNoEQJ.jpg&h=ae59445c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r3eyhCq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr3eyhCq.jpg&h=9447dff7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U8qEXCs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU8qEXCs.jpg&h=dc9f3851&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2cd7b308a489d4c12a26f01ece4101e831d4e1e","tid":1565543,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:48:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=4d4bc680\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各區集合地點!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n油麻地、佐敦、尖沙咀: 梳士巴利公園(太空館附近)<br />\n荃灣、大窩口、青衣: 荃灣公園(海濱長廊)、青衣海濱長廊<br />\n葵興、葵芳、荔景: 林士德遊樂場、葵涌運動場<br />\n美孚: 嶺南之風<br />\n太子、旺角: 花墟公園<br />\n荔枝角、長沙灣: 長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗: 通州街公園<br />\n油塘、藍田: 油塘道遊樂場<br />\n將軍澳、寶琳、坑口、康城<br />\n中西區（西區、中環、金鐘、半山、山頂）<br />\n灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后、炮台山: 維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌、太古、西灣河、筲箕灣: 沿海旁<br />\n小西灣、杏花邨、柴灣: 柴灣公園<br />\n鑽石山、黃大仙: 黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘: 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n大圍、沙田、馬鞍山 : 沙田百步梯<br />\n元朗、天水圍: 天水園公園<br />\n屯門: 屯門公園<br />\n南區: 鴨利洲風之塔公園<br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子山同山頂人鏈!"},{"pid":"c1ec3bef648bd8e20e7f6b76b9939dee7778b80b","tid":1565543,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb72912fd5d18b01ff573f29f1a66cd40553a0da","tid":1565543,"uid":286799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:55:14.000Z","